title: Friday Post Show (02-18-22)
itunes:title: Friday Post Show (02-18-22)
description:
Bobby talks about news he didn’t get to during the show including a woman who changed her name to something unusual because she loves unicorns, Stranger Things coming to an end and Southwest is bringing back alcohol. He also shares a story that he FOR SURE couldn’t talk about on the air. Bobby also finally shares the color blind story he forgot to mention on the show yesterday. Bobby also takes some listener callers.
